data.description: This home offers an abundance of space and features that cater to both comfort and convenience. With four generous bedrooms and three and a half baths, including a master suite on the first floor AND a coveted mother-in-law suite, this home is designed to accommodate diverse lifestyles. As you step inside, you're greeted by a grand two-story foyer, setting the tone for the elegance that unfolds throughout. The soaring ceilings in the great room along with the gas fireplace, create an impressive focal point, bathing the space in natural light and providing a perfect setting for gatherings.  The heart of this home is the well-appointed kitchen, conveniently located off the great room and formal dining room.With brand new SS appliances and abundance of cabinets and counter space, the layout is sure to inspire culinary creations.  The spacious master retreat has an abundance of windows and space for large furniture. The luxurious bath includes a jetted tub, stand alone shower, double vanity and separate water closet. Included on the first floor is a second master bedroom/Mother-in-law suite is comfortable in size and includes a private bath with an oversized shower. A dedicated home office/study ensures a productive workspace, while the second floor offers two large bedrooms and a versatile loft area, providing ample room for relaxation, play, or creative pursuits. The screened porch offers a tranquil retreat, overlooking a picturesque pond, providing a serene backdrop for morning coffees or evening unwinding. Situated on a premium pond lot, the views from this home are simply breathtaking, offering a unique blend of natural beauty and tranquility.  The home has been freshly painted,  new HVAC system, new eat-in kitchen flooring and new kitchen appliances.  A $1,800 Lender Credit is available and will be applied towards the buyer's closing costs and pre-paids if the buyer chooses to use the seller's preferred lender.  This credit is in addition to any negotiated seller concessions.
